Step 1: Prepare the Dataset
Open Excel and load your dataset (Sales Data.xlsx).
Check for Missing Data:
Remove empty rows or incorrect data.
Ensure consistency in column names.
Format the Data Properly:
Convert the Date column to Date Format.
Convert Total Sales (₹) and Price (₹) to Currency Format (₹ Indian Rupee).
Remove duplicates (Data > Remove Duplicates).
Apply Filters to clean and analyze the data easily (Data > Filter).
